Name: Super Blue Boy Planet
About the game: Super Blue Boy Planet is an unusual little platform game with some quirky graphics. You have navigate the levels avoiding obstacles and creepy crawlies. You can jump gaps and also jump on monsters, both destroying them and getting you further in the same move. Jumping also lets you activate bridges and other objects, something you need to do in order to progress. - Gamepad supported and recommended - Different enemies - Level Bosses - Puzzle elements - Easy to play
